# 💘 Love is a Bot Game

A Telegram-based AI-powered variety dating game show where you step into the spotlight as one of 10 contestants (5 guys, 5 girls). Drama, decisions, and digital romance unfold over 5 days!

---

## 🎮 How to Play

- Choose a **character** (any gender, any archetype)
- Set your **drama level** and **location**
- Each day brings scenarios and choices
- Your past decisions **affect future days**
- At the end, make your choice or surprise everyone

---

## ⚙️ Features

- Role selection & archetypes
- Weighted decision-impact system
- Real-time day simulation
- Personality traits & reactions
- End-game summary + shareable message
- Telegram bot interface

---

## 🧠 Built With

- Python `python-telegram-bot`
- Custom game state logic
- Inspired by my favourite classic dating shows with a twist

